[
    {
        "text": "ï»¿For more than two weeks now, the sun has burned down on Japan...",
        "startTime": 160,
        "endTime": 3101,
        "slowStartTime": 390,
        "slowEndTime": 4877
    },
    {
        "text": "...from a cloudless sky with barely a waft of wind.",
        "startTime": 3191,
        "endTime": 6322,
        "slowStartTime": 4937,
        "slowEndTime": 9708
    },
    {
        "text": "Outside the Imperial Palace in Tokyo, the heat shimmer tells its own story.",
        "startTime": 8039,
        "endTime": 12169,
        "slowStartTime": 12209,
        "slowEndTime": 18478
    },
    {
        "text": "Here, the tourists are sweltering in only 37 degrees today.",
        "startTime": 12720,
        "endTime": 16354,
        "slowStartTime": 19230,
        "slowEndTime": 24756
    },
    {
        "text": "A little further north, in the city of Kumagaya, it is considerably hotter.",
        "startTime": 17390,
        "endTime": 21029,
        "slowStartTime": 26235,
        "slowEndTime": 31768
    },
    {
        "text": "The thermometer here hit 41.1 degrees on Monday,...",
        "startTime": 21519,
        "endTime": 24937,
        "slowStartTime": 32429,
        "slowEndTime": 37631
    },
    {
        "text": "...the highest ever recorded anywhere in Japan.",
        "startTime": 25406,
        "endTime": 27930,
        "slowStartTime": 38259,
        "slowEndTime": 42120
    },
    {
        "text": "The heat is not just uncomfortable, it is now extremely dangerous.",
        "startTime": 28928,
        "endTime": 32415,
        "slowStartTime": 43542,
        "slowEndTime": 48847
    },
    {
        "text": "At Tokyo's Emergency Dispatch Center, the calls are coming thick and fast.",
        "startTime": 33150,
        "endTime": 36877,
        "slowStartTime": 49875,
        "slowEndTime": 55541
    },
    {
        "text": "The ambulance crews are struggling to keep up...",
        "startTime": 38383,
        "endTime": 40330,
        "slowStartTime": 57725,
        "slowEndTime": 60720
    },
    {
        "text": "...as across Japan, more than 30,000 people have now been hospitalized...",
        "startTime": 40459,
        "endTime": 44821,
        "slowStartTime": 60838,
        "slowEndTime": 67456
    },
    {
        "text": "...with heatstroke or heat exhaustion.",
        "startTime": 44921,
        "endTime": 46945,
        "slowStartTime": 67531,
        "slowEndTime": 70643
    },
    {
        "text": "The elderly are most at risk.",
        "startTime": 48237,
        "endTime": 49925,
        "slowStartTime": 72506,
        "slowEndTime": 75112
    },
    {
        "text": "More than half of the deaths reported so far have been people over 65.",
        "startTime": 50184,
        "endTime": 54725,
        "slowStartTime": 75426,
        "slowEndTime": 82313
    },
    {
        "text": "In the ancient capital, Kyoto, the summer festivals are underway.",
        "startTime": 56093,
        "endTime": 59819,
        "slowStartTime": 84289,
        "slowEndTime": 89954
    },
    {
        "text": "Here, it has been 38 degrees or more for a solid week, another record.",
        "startTime": 60287,
        "endTime": 65036,
        "slowStartTime": 90581,
        "slowEndTime": 97779
    },
    {
        "text": "All of this is being caused by a huge high pressure dome...",
        "startTime": 66365,
        "endTime": 69649,
        "slowStartTime": 99697,
        "slowEndTime": 104699
    },
    {
        "text": "...that is sitting over the top of Japan and Korea.",
        "startTime": 69893,
        "endTime": 72257,
        "slowStartTime": 104989,
        "slowEndTime": 108610
    },
    {
        "text": "For the last two weeks, it has refused to budge.",
        "startTime": 73201,
        "endTime": 75906,
        "slowStartTime": 109951,
        "slowEndTime": 114084
    },
    {
        "text": "The bad news: it could be here for another two.",
        "startTime": 76481,
        "endTime": 79527,
        "slowStartTime": 114871,
        "slowEndTime": 119515
    }
]